name: live-resume
description: In today's digital age, having an online presence is crucial for professionals across all industries. One way to establish an online presence is by creating a personal portfolio website that showcases your skills, experience, and accomplishments. With the increasing demand for data-driven insights in the business world, business analytics professionals are no exception. This is where the Pradyumna.ie website comes into play, offering a sample portfolio for business analytics professionals to display their works and projects in a straightforward manner.
